c: 2
v: 125
t: "wadhkr -ayha alnby- hin jaealna alkaebat mrjeana llnas, yatwnh, thuma yurjaeun 'iilaa ahlyhm, thuma yaeudun 'ilyh, wmjmeana lahum fi alhaja waleumrat waltwaf walslat, wamnana lhm, la yughir ealayhim eaduun fyh. wqlna: atkhidhu min maqam 'iibrahim mkanana lilsalat fyh, wahu alhajar aldhy waqf ealayh 'iibrahim eind bnayh alkeb. wa'awhayna 'iilaa 'iibrahim wabnh 'ismaeyl: 'an thhira bayti min kuli rijs wdns; llmtebdyn fih baltwaf hawl alkebt, 'aw alaetkaf fi almsjd, walsalat fyh"